description:
Paul Scheer [The Leauge, The Hot Wives of Orlando, Human Giant, NTSF:SD:SUV, Black Monday] is an actor, comedian, writer, director, producer, and podcaster. Paul and Anna have a heartfelt conversation about the events and decisions that shape a life, finding balance, not comparing yourself to others, the power of apologizing, and what it takes to be a terrible parent. Paul also describes how he schedules a shower, the similarities between a medical doctor and a Star Trek Captain, what he looks for in a binge-worthy television show, and more.
